settings.description:
so much sand, with so many coins found deep under such! think you can unearth enough for a nice three extra lives?
don't forget to check what's in the bricks as well!
watch out! this airship's full of plants! odd choice, but maybe the fire they spit is rather effective at keeping plumbers out!
strange spinning spheres with arrows on them! hop on top of such, and go for a ride! think you can use them to your advantage for getting through this cave?
watch out! you're in the middle of a warzone with all these dangerous cannons and Bob-ombs being fired out! think you can find the hidden mad lad as well?
Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.
just like how the real e-reader levels have a two part special that's all about one tough as nails challenge.. instead of an airship, you get a huge castle! watch out, The Big Boo awaits you!
